	   <tr><td colspan=2>A good strategy for human bards is to kill in the newbie fields till lvl 3. Then head on over to EC and kill fire beetles. At lvl 5 go after bears. Kill bears till you lvl and get a hq bear pelt. Then sell it and buy some armor and a new weapon. Then head on over to GFay and kill at orc hill. When you feel that your ready go kill at crushbone till 9. Then go kill dervs in NRo till 10 or 11. Dervs give good ex. and they drop bronze weapons. Next head back to CB and start a Throne Room group. This is a great newbie bard stratigy guid and it kick ass for me.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
